data.description: Welcome to 47 Hybrid Lane, a charming property in Linden, NC. Meticulously maintained, with ALL NEW carpet, new tile, NEW HVAC (June 2023). This lovely home boasts a two car garage, 4 generously sized bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, a formal dining room, and a large great room featuring a gas fireplace. All bedrooms are located on the second floor. Primary suite has a beautiful trey ceiling with ceiling fan, large garden tub, separate shower, private commode and large walk-in closet! Laundry room is conveniently located on second floor. The open floor plan and natural lighting make for a bright and inviting atmosphere, while the spacious backyard offers ample space for outdoor activities. Home is situated on a large level lot with a privacy fence. Home is on septic and was pumped 1/12/2024. Sweetwater subdivision offers a peaceful country setting and is only 15 minutes to Manchester Gate on Fort Liberty. No city taxes!
